text: Djamel El Okbi (15 October 1939 – 15 December 1994) was a professional Algerian footballer who played as a Goalkeeper for USM Alger. ==Life and career== ==Honours== ** Championnat National *** Winner: 1962-63 ==Clubs== * AS Saint-Eugènoise (1957–1960) * USM Alger (1962–1969) ==References== ==External links== Category:1939 births Category:1994 deaths Category:Algerian footballers Category:Ligue 1 players Category:Footballers from Algiers Category:USM Alger players Category:People from Kouba Category:Association football goalkeepers
